{"tid":671615,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"坐飛機你就坐得多，咁你到底知唔知個機師牌點考？","createTime":"2018-05-20T09:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T19:36:31.000Z","uid":156394,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a104286966737538adf86a037b86f7297e1e7fa1","tid":671615,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"係澳洲飛機師牌就分四種，分別係RPL、PPL、CPL同ATPL。<br />\n有興趣可以睇下呢條片，五分鐘就明白晒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kT5icgrNzpU&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkT5icgrNzpU%26t%3D1s&d=gvcWd9NFaIJSdc%2B8%2FS%2Fdbrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=5eb919b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kT5icgrNzpU&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n無興趣就自己睇以下文字：<br />\n<br />\nRPL: 娛樂機師證書 <br />\nPPL: 私人機師牌照 <br />\nCPL: 商業機師牌照 (澳洲牌例不需要雙引擎及儀表飛行也可以考取CPL)<br />\n **影片中的價錢是培訓生CPL的價錢、裡頭含了MCC訓練、ATPL所有的理論、儀表及雙引擎訓練、指定班號認可(如波音787或A350的)。 <br />\n<br />\n一般只考取CPL的成本約8萬澳幣。 <br />\n<br />\nMPL: 多組員機師牌照 <br />\nATPL: 國際民航機師照牌 <br />\nIREX: 儀表飛行認可<br />\n<br />\n＊反正你都無興趣，直接上一頁啦不如洗咩睇其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4529ec900ddd22675b64f04d2ad2c44e85ea7f6","tid":671615,"uid":101197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有個人唔識揸飛機，到最後害死埋個教練 。"},{"pid":"a49c5ffff50a6e152c788a81362ba145252855a4","tid":671615,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4529ec900ddd22675b64f04d2ad2c44e85ea7f6","tid":671615,"uid":101197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有個人唔識揸飛機，到最後害死埋個教練 。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:00:36.000Z","msg":"邏輯有問題，做得教練坐隔離果個肯定唔識揸架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以其實應該係個教練自己害死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c0507dc9fe707c5ba45ba292fb07078d774178","tid":671615,"uid":109408,"like":0,"disl